Reese!
[sighs]

28:43.983 --> 28:46.594
This guy has won.

28:46.637 --> 28:48.683
I'm telling you this
as your friend.

28:48.727 --> 28:50.163
If you don't

28:50.206 --> 28:52.469
let this go, it's going to be
the end of your career.

29:00.434 --> 29:02.349
♪ Are you ready
for the Devil, man? ♪

29:02.392 --> 29:05.134
♪ Are you ready for
the Devil, man? ♪

29:05.178 --> 29:09.008
♪ Are you ready
